title: Let's Do the Time War Again
description: Ben, Skurd and Rook find themselves caught in an endless time loop as enemies from the future converge on Bellwood.

title: Captain Bamboozle
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk decides to create some mischief by endowing Shazam's well-meaning Uncle Dudley with superpowers bigger than anyone in the league.

title: Food Chain
description: On a field trip to the Candy Kingdom Museum of Natural History, Finn and Jake learn about the food chain by becoming the food chain!

title: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit/Secrets Exposed
description: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit: It's time for the event everyone in Los Volmos has been waiting for, The Bakugan Battle League finals! It's the Awesome Brawler's Dan Kouzo vs. the golden Bakugan brawler Ajit, these two face-off in a final brawl for it all./Secrets Exposed: The Bakugan Battle League has ended, and the winner has been determined, but the celebration is cut short when Phantom Thief Storm crashes the party by stealing everyone's Bakugan! It's up to Dan and Ajit to stop Storm and return all the stolen Bakugan.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Pop a Wheelie
description: Thomas and Diesel take a friendly competition too far and put an important delivery rescue at risk as they race across Sodor.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Los Supervillanso se Unen
description: Después de una pausa en las payasadas alienígenas, un inquieto Ben les sugiere a Max y Gwen que podría ser un mejor héroe si fuera solo. Pero cuando Vilgax consigue la ayuda de Zombozo para construir un mecanismo hipnotizador gigante para hipnotizar al mundo entero, Ben debe replantearse su estrategia si quiere derrotar al equipo de supervillanos.

title: Terra-ized
description: Beast Boy falls for Terra despite clear signs that she is more interested in destroying the Titans.

title: That Ol' Time Rock Rolls!/Make Like a Banana and Split
description: When Big Old Boulder rolls down the hill towards the museum, Berta needs the Mechas help to keep it stable./It's Food Day in Pretty Big City, but the Mechas need to help when the banana atop the banana split statue is not split!

title: Take Us Out to the Ballgame
description: The Baby Looney Tunes experience their very first big stadium baseball game. Lola's favorite team's star batter gets her undivided attention until Lola's coaching affects the very outcome of the contest.

title: Last One There
description: When Unikitty accidentally invokes an ancient curse, the gang must beat Master Frown and Brock back to the castle before one of them literally turns into a rotten egg.

title: Teddi Bear
description: In an endless junkyard the Bears meet Teddi, a sentient teddy bear.

title: The Future is Cardboard
description: The kids meet an eccentric Cardboard Creator that invites Craig to help finish his masterpiece.

title: Fall of the Fifth Sun
description: With the help of a few trusted allies, Victor and Valentino provoke a final confrontation with Tez which leaves the fate of Monte Macabre hanging in the balance!

title: Oh, Daisy!
description: Buttercup is not a fan of Bubbles' newly created digital assistant.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Angry Alien
description: An angry alien finds his way to Pocoyo's world and declares that he wants to be king. Pocoyo, Elly and Caterpillar are all friendly but the alien just bosses them around and tries to scare them. When the alien tells Pato what to do, Pato finds it rather helpful. This goes against what the alien was expecting. Finally the alien is upset because he's not getting the reaction he wanted. He sobs and sobs. Pocoyo et al are concerned and kind. The alien realizes that he is likable, and if he'd just stop being so angry, he could have fun.

title: Swing
description: Bing and Pando are taking turns on the swing. Bing counts to ten, but will Pando do the same?

title: Land of the Lost Shadows
description: When pieces of their shadows are stolen by a shadow demon, Uncle Grandpa and the gang must travel to the Land of Lost Shadows in order to retrieve them.

title: Sad Face
description: Once a month, while Jake's asleep, his tail stretches out of the treehouse to go work as a clown in a traveling bug circus.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Secrets
description: Grandpa Max's mysterious past comes to light when Vilgax shows up on earth in search of the Omnitrix. And the family must work together to defeat him.

title: Fragments
description: Steven heads to the woods to train with a powerful mentor.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Clues Encounters of the Tweety Kind
description: Tweety feels neglected when no one wants him on their museum scavenger hunt team. Using his innate sleuthing abilities and the help of a friendly museum guard, Tweety proves to be the best scavenger hunter of them all. Once Tweety wins the contest, everyone wants him on their team.

title: The Unikingdom Awards
description: Unikitty throws an elaborate award show for everyone in the Unikingdom, including Master Frown and Brock, but tensions rise when Frown fails to win an award.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Collect Her/Supper Villain
description: Collect Her: A fan of the Powerpuff Girls has collected every bit of Powerpuff stuff available, almost. His collection will be complete with three more items./Supper Villain: The girls' neighbor reveals he's not exactly the nice guy next door. But how will they capture him during a seemingly innocent dinner party?

title: Just Wait in the Car
description: As Mary runs errands, Clarence waits in the car and struggles to fight boredom.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Brood
description: Craig's determination to get his granddad a cicada shell causes him, Kelsey and JP to become trapped in their stump!

title: From Hedorium to Eternity
description: 11-year-old Ben, Gwen, and friends go on the adventure of a lifetime in their own backyard.

title: One Step Forward, Two Steps Back
description: When the ninja learn that the only way to acquire the second Key-tana is by winning a dangerous race in Terra Technica they'll have to find some racing cars in unexpected ways.

title: The Big Freeze
description: The Bears investigate the mysterious transformation of a tropical valley into a winter wonderland of snow. To return it to its natural state, Funshine must follow Dibble's example and give up something he wanted for himself.

title: Watch the Storm
description: When Chep asks Mush-Mush and Lilit to go storm-watching and they refuse, Lilit feels bad and convinces Mush-Mush to join their friend. But there are no storms on the horizon. When they notice Chanterelle going through the forest mysteriously, our Mushlers decide to find out what she's up to instead. That's when a big storm starts brewing on the horizon.

title: #Powerless
description: Supergirl loses her powers and, with the help of BumbleBee, must rely on her street smarts to save Garth from vengeful Toyman.

title: Nuggets de Pollo de Sabiduria
description: Cuando Ben y Max comienzan a discutir, Ben se convierte en Fuego para desahogarse, contra la voluntad de Max. Pero una vez que el Dr. Animo lo ve y convierte a Max en un pollo, Ben debe enmendar su error si quiere salvar a su Abuelo y detener al Dr. Animo.

title: House Flies Don't Dance/Flying the Nest/The Insult
description: Lucas and Maizie help Findley learn to dance./ Arlo believes he's a big owl now, so it's time to fly his nest. But is Arlo ready to leave his friends behind?/ When Lucas calls Findley a mean name, he tries to make things right again.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: The Prank
description: Gumball and Darwin's harmless pranks on Dad spiral hopelessly out of control.

title: Video Cita
description: Panda es un ávido salidor de citas por Internet, y cuando una adorable mujer francesa coincide con él y accede a tener una cita virtual con video, Panda y sus hermanos manejan la situación para poder mostrar su mejor perfil en el video, aunque ese perfil sea absolutamente exagerado.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Video Date
description: Panda is an avid e-dater, and when a lovely French woman matches with him and agrees to a video chat date. Panda and his brothers engineer the situation so Panda is able to show the best side of himself on the video chat, even if that side of him is completely exaggerated.

title: The Best Friend/Thief and Brawler
description: The Best Friend: The top four brawlers in the Bakugan Battle League have been decided. For this round of the semi-finals it's a battle of best friends: Wynton vs. Dan. The winner of this battle between best buddies will move on to the championship round./Thief and Brawler: In the final battle of the Bakugan Battle league semi-finals it's Shun vs. Ajit. It's a grueling battle of focus, will, and strength, only a true brawler to emerge victorious.

title: #WarriorAndTheJester
description: After accidentally destroying one of Babs' beloved, one-of-a-kind Batman keepsakes, Diana enlists the help of Harleen Quinzel in order to find a replacement in Gotham City.

title: Ducks
description: Bing and Sula are feeding the ducks in the park, but will Bing remember to stand statue still?

title: Shutterbug
description: Pocoyo, Elly and Baby Bird are bored of Pato's countless flower photos so they encourage him to take pictures of them instead. But each time Pato takes a photo, someone moves. Pato is exasperated because he wants to take perfect portraits but there's always something not quite right. Pato gives up. His friends put on an exhibition of his photos to show him that his pictures may not be exactly what he had in mind, but they really are wonderful because they capture the fun the friends have together.

title: Mr. Universe
description: Greg takes Steven on the road to find the origins of the Universe name.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Crack the Whip
description: Amethyst is left in charge of Steven and Connie, and there will be no training while she's around!

title: Forever Ever
description: When Vic and Val do a sloppy job cleaning up in Maria Theresa's attic, they accidentally set off a time loop, trapping them in an endless series of chores forever! They must figure out how to stop the loop and return time back to normal.

title: Xochi's Garden
description: When Vic and Val accidentally bring a fungus into Xochi's garden, they have to find a way to stop the monstrous plants it creates.

title: Stuck Up, Up and Away/Schoolhouse Rocked
description: Stuck Up, Up and Away: Bratty little Princess comes to town and wants to be a Powerpuff Girl. When she doesn't get what she wants, the girls will have to pay./Schoolhouse Rocked: The Gangreen Gang goes back to school at Pokey Oaks Kindergarten and become the school bullies. Since the girls can't fight in school, how can they stop them?

title: Gem Hunt
description: Steven and Connie track a Gem monster through the wilderness but its tracks lead them to mystery.

title: My Stare Lady
description: Craig enters a dangerous staring contest, hoping to win another one of Kenneth's Cubes.

title: High Baby Fashion
description: The Bears enter Panda into a fashion contest, but he's got some fierce competition when Madam Malin and Madeline show up!

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: The Castle
description: When Mom is away "anything goes" and Dad's lack of rules soon attracts unwelcome houseguests.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: #TheMinus
description: Diana receives her first ever A minus and becomes convinced that she needs to work harder, however, in order to do so, she resorts to rather drastic measures.

title: Third Time's a Charm
description: Charmaster returns to exact her revenge on Gwendolyn once and for all.

title: Happy Place
description: Time to share some of the honey made at Lellobee City Farm with everyone that visits the farm

title: The Prince Who Wanted Everything
description: The beautiful and sensitive Lumpy Space Prince flees his cruel parents to start a new life.

title: The Director/Queen Ebony
description: The Director: Everett Ray reaches out to Lia with an opportunity that seems too good to be true. Everett is now working in show business and proposes to make Lia's dream of becoming a film director come true. He's taken care of all the arrangements; all Lia has to do is provide the directorial vision./Queen Ebony: On his daily jaunt, Lightning learns of a street cat named Ebony, who's been treating dogs like servants, threatening them to do her bidding or face the wrath of her Bakugan! Lightning tries to reason with Ebony but when that doesn't work, it turns into a cat vs. dog Bakugan brawl!

title: Into the Obsidian
description: When Victor and Valentino discover that Tez has been spying on the citizens of Monte Macabre, they vow to expose his treachery!

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Chocolate Factory
description: Blippi's love for chocolate makes him wonder "How are chocolate bars made?" They head into a chocolate factory to find out, get a tour from Bard the Chocolate Bar, and FETCH gets a close-up look at the chocolate-making process!

title: All Koiled Up
description: When Ben grows impatient with the snail like pace of gardening, he goes O-E Overflow to pick up the pace and accidentally floods the community garden, but once a giant sink hole appears and frees King Koil and his Kimodo Dragon from below, Ben must quickly right his wrong and capture the baddies if he is to save the coastal city of Bayburgh.

title: Magnet Mayhem/Stop That Train
description: The magnet crane at the construction site accidentally turns on, sucking up all the metal, including the Mecha Builders!/Roof is delivering eggs to Marwyn at the Train Station, that is, until the train pulls into the station and can't stop!

title: Escape de Bahia Bebe
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic y Val se convierten a sí mismos y a Don en bebés, deben escapar de una guardería para poder volver a sus edades normales.

title: Beat Your Greens/Down N' Dirty
description: Beat Your Greens: When Broccoli Aliens from space invade Townsville, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls and all the children of Townsville to take a bite out of crime. Down N' Dirty: When Buttercup refuses to take a bath, the town kicks her out. But Buttercup decides to stick with her stink until her favorite thing is taken away from her.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Scoutguest
description: Craig finds himself with an unlikely house guest when Jason the Junior Forest Scout sleeps over.

title: La Camada
description: La determinación de Craig de conseguirle a su abuelo un caparazón de cigarra hace que él, Kelsey y JP queden atrapados en su tronco.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Goodbye, Ghost-Scaring Machine
description: Percy announces he's giving up his Ghost Scaring Machine - he's too old for it now. It soon becomes clear that the machine is good for more than just "scaring ghosts."
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Best Best Friends
description: Master Frown and Brock attend a friendship-themed competition intending to ruin it for everyone else, but soon discover their own friendship in need of repair.

title: Truth
description: An old Plumber partner of Max's resurfaces with nefarious intentions and ends up stealing the dangerous Null Void Projector.

title: Lonely Haunts Club 4: La Pablita
description: Victor and Valentino accompany Charlene and Pineapple to burned down bridal shop with an eerie mannequin in the window. Charlene insists the place is not haunted, but the boys have their doubts.

title: Missing Cat
description: When Chelsea accidentally lets her pet cat Crumbles out, the cat goes missing! Reluctant to ask for help, she struggles to find the cat before anyone realizes it's gone. It's up to cat whisperer Clarence to interject and find Crumbles, whether Chelsea wants his help or not!

title: The Tower
description: Finn doesn't like any of the new arms the princesses give him so he builds a tower into space to find his dad and get his old arm back.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Chloe and Ice Bear
description: On a day out with just Ice Bear, Chloe realizes Ice Bear only runs errands for his brothers. Determined to show him a fun day in the city, Chloe promises to help Ice Bear have a good time, even if it means staying  in a museum after it closes.

title: NBTS 2: Chapter Two
description: In order to stop Ultralak, the Titans must find three music stems, but will need help from a local Miner to get the first stem away from the Sheriff.

title: Pobrecito Pete
description: When Valentino carelessly poisons Gustavo's horse, he must find a cure to absolve his secret guilt.

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: Banda de por Vida
description: Cuando Vic y Val acompañan a Xochi a un concierto punk, quieren demostrar que son lo suficientemente geniales para salir con ella. Pero en un intento desesperado por tener onda, terminan arruinando el concierto.

title: Now Museum, Now You Don't
description: Their very first trip to an art museum unleashes creative energy, turning the Baby Looney Tunes into enthused culture connoisseurs and budding artists. Baby Bugs recreates the museum experience back at Granny's house, finding abundant art history in everyday objects to the others' sheer delight.

title: Tez dice
description: Vic y Val están impresionados con el nuevo mago de la ciudad, pero las cosas se complican cuando aceptan ayudarlo con un nuevo truco, a pesar de los deseos de Chata.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: La Tienda De Cupcakes
description: Quando o adorado computador dos ursos quebra, os três são obrigados a fazer algo que nunca haviam feito antes: arrumar um emprego. Eles começam a trabalhar numa loja badalada de cupcakes e se dão conta de que o mercado profissional é muito mais penoso do que achavam.

title: These Little Piggies Went to Market
description: Their first trip to a big grocery store fascinates the Baby Looney Tunes. After warning the others to stick to Granny's shopping list, Baby Bugs succumbs to buying a favorite treat then feels guilty.

title: The Return of Aunt Grandma
description: Aunt Grandma is back and still bent on ruining Uncle Grandpa.

title: Un Paso Adelante, Dos Pasos Atras
description: La única manera de que los Ninjas obtengan segunda Keytana es ganando una carrera en Tierra Technica y tiene que conseguir autos de carreras para eso.

title: Win That Prize
description: Pops wants to go on his favorite game show Win That Prize but instead gets deeply involved in the television industry.

title: Pizza Eve
description: Uncle Grandpa falls for Pizza Steve's "girlfriend" and ends up in serious danger.

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Mountain
description: Blippi and TABBS head off on an icy adventure and fly up the side of Mt. Everest, the world's tallest mountain! They are joined by Betty the Yeti who is climbing to the top of the mountain in search of the ultimate snack - fresh snow!

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Super-Villain Team-Up
description: After a lull in alien antics, a restless Ben suggests to Max and Gwen that he might be a better hero if he went solo, but once Vilgax enlists the help of Zombozo to build a giant hypno-mechanism to hypnotize the entire world, Ben must rethink his strategy if he is to defeat the super-villain team-up.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sr. Universo
description: Greg lleva a Steven de viaje para encontrar los orígenes del nombre del Universo.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Oneiric Vic
description: In an encounter with a mysterious child more helpless than himself, Victor must summon tremendous intelligence, courage and empathy.

title: A Dame-gerous Game
description: After Leshawna, Bridgette, Owen and Cody win a Hide & Seek competition, they're trapped on a private island by a jealous former champion and forced to play for their freedom.

title: The Secret of Dos Santos
description: Ben and Rook join Kai Green on a perilous alien relic hunt through South America.

title: #MultipliciZee
description: Zee magically duplicates herself so she can shirk work and watch TV. Things get out of hand when her copies start to make copies of themselves!

title: Alone at Sea
description: Steven and Greg take a boat trip out to sea and find themselves in dangerous water.

title: Inodoro Real
description: Cuando los otros chicos temen que Harold se haya descargado a sí mismo por accidente en el elegante inodoro nuevo de Chef, viajan al desagüe a rescatarlo. Pero, ¿encontrarán a Harold antes que el mítico Cocodrilo Rey los deje atrapados bajo tierra para siempre?

title: Todo Enrollado
description: Cuando Ben se impacienta con el ritmo lento de la jardinería, se convierte en O-E Overflow para acelerar las cosas y, por accidente, inunda el jardín de la comunidad.

title: The Escape Room of Doom
description: The gang infiltrate an escape room game center to thwart Score Creeper, but their former foe claims he only works there to pay the bills.

title: Bajo el Puente
description: Craig y sus amigos viajan para encontrar madreselva en el arroyo, pero descubren una parte completamente nueva del arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Piloto Siete
description: Mientras los Ninjas se preparan para la carrera Cinco Billones por Hora, Lloyd conoce a la Piloto Siete quien puede tener la clave de la victoria.

title: King Koil
description: Ben and Gwen spend the day volunteering at Repto Ranch and come face to face with King Koil, but need to quickly overcome their fear of snakes if they are to rescue the released critters and defeat the slithery baddie.

title: Eternamente
description: Cuando Vic y Val limpian el ático de María Teresa a medias, ipor accidente inician un bucle de tiempo que los atrapa en una serie interminable de tareas eternas! Ahora deben averiguar cómo detener el bucle y devolver el tiempo a la normalidad.

title: Sneaky Shoes
description: Pato, Pocoyo and Elly are having fun doing running and jumping competitions: except Pato is taking it very seriously. So when he loses he's mighty miffed. He is a very bad loser. He goes off in a huff and finds some swanky sneakers. He tries them on and discovers that these are no ordinary sneakers: they have a life of their own, they have super powers. Once he's mastered them he challenges Pocoyo and Elly to a re-match. Of course now he wins the running and jumping contests hands down. But Elly feels that something's up and doesn't want to compete anymore. When Pato tries to take the shoes off he realizes they won't undo. He's stuck and the shoes are going crazy. Luckily Caterpillar and Baby Bird save the day by getting the shoes off. And Pato has learnt that cheating just isn't a good way to win.

title: Mission Mariachi
description: Unable to get tickets to see his favorite mariachi band, Val, with the help of Isabella, attempts to meet the Mariachi Reyna De Los Angeles by any means necessary.

title: #AcceptNoSubstitute
description: Feeling smothered, Babs urges her retired dad, Commissioner Gordon, to get a hobby, but her advice backfires when the Commissioner becomes a substitute teacher at her school!

title: The Streak Part 1
description: It's Crime Season and Robin is determined to continue his streak of stopping 52 crimes every year.

title: Band For Life
description: When Vic and Val tag along with Xochi to a punk concert, they want to prove that they're cool enough to hang out with her. But in a desperate attempt to be cool, they wind up destroying the concert.

title: El futuro es de Carton
description: Los niños conocen a un excéntrico Creador de Cartón que invita a Craig a ayudarlo a terminar su obra maestra.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: NBTS 2: Chapter One
description: The elderly Titans decide to take one last trip to the world of Night Begins to Shine only to encounter a new villian ruling the land, Ultralak.

title: Pato's Paintings
description: Everyone's preparing for a painting exhibition. Everyone except Pato who says he's not bothered about painting. When the show opens, Pato unexpectedly exhibits his paintings: they are amazing masterpieces (Actually they are real masterpieces. He didn't paint them!). Everyone is very impressed and asks him to paint another. But he can't, because in fact he cheated: he didn't paint these pictures at all. Pocoyo and the audience encourage Pato to have a go at painting. He paints a beautiful flower and feels very pleased with himself. His painting takes its place in the exhibition.

title: Chicken Nuggets of Wisdom
description: When Ben and Max get into an argument, Ben goes Heatblast to blow off steam against Max's wishes; but once Dr. Animo spots him and subsequently turns Max into a chicken, it's up to Ben to right his wrong if he is to save his Grandpa and stop Dr. Animo.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Big Tick
description: A giant alien tick that sucks planets dry, lands on Earth with the sole purpose of destroying the planet and only a new alien hero can stop it.

title: Messy Bessy
description: Seth must clean his room and learn to be a neater person in order to keep Messy Bessy from making his life a nightmare.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Pet Shop
description: Pet Shop tells the tale of where the Baby Bears once lived, and after a run-in with a video crew shooting a Sarah McLachlan-type animal adoption video, almost seized an opportunity to find a home separated from each other.

title: Here Comes Haavik/The Fusion Bakugan Arrive
description: Here Comes Haavik: An evil shapeshifting alien has landed in Los Volmos! If that wasn't bad enough, he has a group of robot mechanoids on his trail trying to bring him justice. Meanwhile, Dan has accepted a battle challenge from a pair of brawlers, Chad and Trey./The Fusion Bakugan Arrive: Still humiliated by their defeat, Chad and Trey challenge Dan to rematch but this time they have a few tricks up their sleeve, and a little help on their side.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: Tez Says
description: Vic & Val are in awe of the new magician in town, but things go awry when they agree to help him out with a new trick - despite Chata's wishes.

title: Frog
description: Bing and Sula find a frog in the garden, but will Froggy like her new bucket house?

title: O'Little Tree
description: Mei shows Ella and Rishi the magic of Christmas - by growing an adorable Christmas tree in the middle of the farm.

title: Chloe Y Polar
description: Un día, Chloe sale sola a pasear con Polar y se da cuenta de que Polar se la pasa haciéndoles recados a sus hermanos. Decidida a mostrarle cómo pasarla bien en la ciudad, Chloe promete ayudar a que Polar se divierta... Aunque eso signifique quedarse dentro de un museo después de la hora de cierre.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Dream Scheme/You Snooze, You Lose
description: Dream Scheme: The Sandman would like a little rest so he puts the world to sleep. The girls must battle him in his dreams to get things back to normal./You Snooze, You Lose: When the Amoeba Boys find Mojo's plan to destroy the Powerpuff Girls, the girls unwittingly help them build a machine for their own destruction.

title: Wake Up
description: In order to find Finn's father, Finn and Jame must commit a cosmic crime unless the Lich beats them to it.

title: Hibernacion
description: Por ser un grupo urbano, los Osos jamás escucharon hablar de la idea de hibernar, hasta que Chloe les cuenta al respecto. Pardo, a quien le encanta la idea de comer mucho y luego dormir todo lo que se le dé la gana, se entrega a la hibernación sin pensarlo. Pero está tan entusiasmado con la idea de hibernar... que no se puede dormir.

title: Cupcake Job
description: When the Bears' beloved laptop breaks, they finally have the need to do something they've never done before: get jobs. Working at a trendy cupcake shop, the Bears find  that the working world is much tougher than they realized.

title: The Laziest
description: Gumball and Darwin challenge Dad to a "lazy-off."

title: Greg the Babysitter
description: Steven learns the tale of how Greg came to work at the car wash.

title: Hello China
description: In order to get high school credits, Rigby has to pass a foreign language class taught by Benson in China.

title: Star Child
description: A conflicted Isabella is faced with the decision of following ruthless orders, or helping her friends.

title: Sophie, the Bakuganist/Midnight Train Battle!
description: Sophie, the Bakuganist: Magnus is on the trail of the illegal Baku-brawling devices and, is looking to cut off the supply at its source. When he witnesses an illegal deal going down, he knows it's up to him to go after the shipment to keep the illegal devices off the street./Midnight Train Battle!: Sophie Judson Warfield, a wealthy activist with the Citizens to Save Bakugan Society, is working to put an end to all Bakugan brawling. Her latest target is the Awesome Brawlers themselves. When Wynton doesn't take Sophie seriously, the encounter quickly turns into an all-out Bakugan brawl.

title: Burger's Trampoline
description: After learning that Burger has a trampoline, Apple and Onion pay him a visit. Burger thinks they came especially to see him and is overjoyed.

title: Blocks
description: Bing is building a tower with his blocks but what will happen when both he and Coco want the last red block?

title: Tienda De Mascotas
description: En este episodio sobre los primeros años de vida de los Osos, se cuenta la historia del lugar en el que vivieron alguna vez cuando eran bebés. Luego de un altercado con el equipo que filmaba un video absolutamente conmovedor de adopción de animales, los Osos por poco aprovechan la oportunidad de encontrar hogares alejados uno del otro.

title: Apple's in Charge
description: Apple is put in charge of the Dollar Store for the very first time.

title: Cool Guy Clarence
description: When Clarence meets JT, the kid who mows their lawn, he finds a fast friend who shows him some cool new music, a new outlook on life and a sweet rat-tail! Clarence leans into the rat tail lifestyle, discovering a whole new side of Aberdale he never knew existed.

title: The Cliffs of Hysteria
description: While being chased by Unagami's dreaded Red Visors the ninja must climb the 'Cliffs of Hysteria', however, they make a startling discovery: Unagami is converting players into energy cubes in order to build a portal into the real world!

title: Un Juego Peligroso
description: Después de que Leshawna, Bridgette, Owen y Cody ganan una competencia de jugar al escondite, están atrapados en una isla privada por una antigua campeona celosa y tienen que jugar a su juego.

title: Snow Tubing
description: Rigby wants Eileen to go snow tubing.

title: Racer Seven
description: As the ninja prepare for the brutal Speedway Five-Billion race, Lloyd meets a race driver named Seven, who is programmed to lose, but who may hold the key to victory.

title: The Debt
description: Gumball resolves to save Mr Robinson's life during Elmore's Senior Talent Show.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: A Bully for Bugs
description: With Floyd's adult assistance, Baby Bugs and the Baby Looney Tunes learn an effective way to deal with a bully.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Baila Reynaldo Baila
description: Vic está desesperado por ganar el premio en efectivo para el concurso de baile en Monte Macabro y está frustrado porque Val, su pareja, no le deja tomar todas las decisiones. Por eso, elige un compañero diferente: Reynaldo. Pero Vic presiona demasiado a Reynaldo para hacer realidad su visión artística. Al final, Vic aprende que, para tener éxito, hay que ser socios en igualdad de condiciones.

title: Keeping Up with the Kryptonians
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk shows Supergirl and Superman that their innate goodness might not be so pure when he takes them to a parallel world where their counterparts are impossibly aggressive and spoiled.

title: Total Eclipse of the Fart
description: After accidentally swallowing her first loose tooth and fearing that means no cash under the pillow, Leshawna tries to capture the tooth fairy. Instead, she accidentally captures the fart fairy. This comes with great consequence.

title: Big Trouble in Little Aberdale
description: After stumbling upon a mysterious new kid in their neighborhood , Clarence, Jeff and Sumo decide to take the kid out on the town showing him the fun of junk food, arcades and soda! However, this new lifestyle may be more then the new kid bargained for.

title: Relaxation Land
description: Uncle Grandpa's relaxing weekend getaway quickly becomes a spooky nightmare for Pizza Steve.

title: Race Track Race
description: The Looney Builders race against the clock to build Cecil Turtle a new racetrack. Daffy gets caught up in his own desire to race and changes part of the build.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: Can I Keep It?
description: After stumbling upon a cute cat-dog-rabbit creature hybrid, or "Cadobbit," Ben ignores Grandpa Max's advice and sneaks the animal onto the Rustbucket, but is quickly in over his head as Dr. Amino's creation turns on him!

title: Escape From Bebe Bay
description: When Vic & Val accidentally turn themselves and Don into babies, they must escape a daycare center in order to change back to their normal ages.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Vic-lene
description: It's a Vic and Charlene switch things up when Vic desperately wants to join a secretive members-only club that Charlene is a part of.

title: Steven vs. Amethyst
description: Steven and Amethyst get competitive while training with Pearl.

title: Witch's Crew
description: On Halloween Night, Morbucks summons a monster that she didn't expect.

title: Chili Cook-Off
description: Benson wants to get some street cred with the Park Managers' Association and win the big chili cook-off.

title: Be Claws I Love You, Shelley
description: When Owen bring a lobster in for show and tell we discover that Chef has a real lobster problem.

title: Royal Flush
description: When the other kids fear Harold has accidentally flushed himself down Chef's fancy new toilet, they travel into the sewer on a rescue mission. But will they find Harold before the mythical Alligator King traps them underground forever?

title: Not Funny
description: With their 6 month friend anniversary approaching, Apple is in danger of losing his best friend.

title: Say What?
description: When Share magically has her voice stolen from her in a field of flowers, she and the other Bears must learn to listen so they can find her voice and solve the problem between the flowers and their Whiffle gardeners.

title: Stuck on You
description: Kybher, aided by a booger-like slime biot named Skurd, attacks Ben & co, but the tables turn when Skurd gloms onto Ben!

title: Smoothie
description: It's snack time, but what will Bing and Flop make with the mushy banana?

title: Run, Mushpie, Run
description: Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit notice that Mushpie seems in great shape lately. They want to feel as great as she does and try to discover her secret. When they realise that she works out every morning, our friends decide to join her. And soon, all the Mushables do too. Now Lilit notices that Mushpie doesn't seem in such great shape anymore.

title: El Hada de los Gases
description: Después de perder su primer diente flojo por accidente y temer el no tener efectivo bajo la almohada, Leshawna intenta capturar al hada de los dientes. En vez de eso, captura al hada de los gases. Esto trae grandes consecuencias.

title: Lights Out!
description: When Bliss brings a new tech product to town, it's more powerful than imagined.

title: Crazy Fake Plan
description: Rigby has to create a massively crazy fake plan in order to surprise Eileen for the first time ever.

title: She Wore Red Velvet
description: When Booster and the JLA come under attack by a mysterious and unrelenting new villainess known as Red Velvet, Booster comes to realize she's actually the fiance he left at the altar in the future.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Baby Boi TP
description: Apple and Onion run out of toilet paper because Apple's been building a huge modern art sculpture with it. They're going to need more if Apple is to finish and Onion is to be able to resume his normal toilet activities.

title: Ice Creamed
description: It's Taz's birthday, so The Looney Builders build him a huge ice cream sundae. Porky worries about making a mistake and delays the build causing the ice cream to start to melt.

title: Unleashed
description: While the Justice League is away on a mission, Plastic Man is not only left in charge of the Watchtower, but also Superman's dog, Krypto.

title: The Glitch
description: In order to stop Unagami the ninja must obtain three Key-tanas, the first of which is hidden in the game zone Terra Kerana, one of Prime Empire's most dangerous game environments.

title: Dance Reynaldo Dance
description: Vic is desperate to win the cash prize for the dance contest in Monte Macabre and is frustrated that his partner Val won't let him call all the shots. Instead he chooses a different partner: Reynaldo. But Vic pushes Reynaldo too hard to execute his artistic vision. Eventually he learns that in order to be a success, you have to be equal partners.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Under the Overpass
description: Craig and his friends travel to find honeysuckle in the creek but discover a whole new part of the creek.

title: The Scoop
description: The Titans find it odd when Starfire becomes friends with an ice cream scoop.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Total Trauma Rama
description: Duncan, normally the bad kid, has an identity crisis when his pranks start curing people of their fears.

title: A Simpler Life: Ayohuih Nemilitzli
description: Valentino gets his wish for a simpler life when he and Vic are transported back to the time of the Aztecs , however he soon discovers life back then might not be as simple as it seems.

title: La Falla
description: Para detener a Unagami, los Ninjas debe obtener 3 Keytanas, la primera está escondida en Tierra Karana, uno de los entornos de juego más peligrosos.

title: Dare Day
description: With Jeff on vacation, Sumo and Clarence egg each other on in a series of increasingly absurd and extreme dares. But will one of them put a stop to this dare day, before it goes too far?

title: Hibernation
description: The bears, being an urban bunch, hadn't ever heard of the idea of hibernation until Chloe tells them about it. Grizz, loving the idea of eating a ton and then just sleeping to his heart's content, goes for it with reckless abandon.  But Grizz is so excited for hibernating... that he can't fall asleep.

title: Puedo Quedarmelo?
description: Tras toparse con una adorable criatura, híbrido de gato, perro y conejo, Ben no hace caso al consejo del abuelo Max y se lleva al animal a escondidas al Chatarra. Pero pronto empiezan los problemas porque ila creación del Dr. Animal lo delata!

title: I'll Do it in a Minute/Cloud Gazing/Don't Do That Arlo
description: Arlo has fun playing, but he procrastinates when it comes to tidying up./ Lucas, Arlo, and Findley have a day of make-believe with the clouds./ Arlo can't resist the temptation to look into next door's garden through a knothole.

title: Barehanded
description: When Green Lantern leaves his ring in an intergalactic restroom after washing his hands, he discovers it's gone, leading him on a wild chase for the aliens who might have taken it.

title: Fragmentos
description: Steven se dirige al bosque para entrenarse con un poderoso mentor.

title: The Limit
description: The Watterson family faces Mom's wrath in a supermarket.

title: Rey Koil
description: Ben y Gwen pasan el día como voluntarios en Repto Ranch y se enfrentan cara a cara con el Rey Koil. Pero necesitan superar rápidamente su miedo a las serpientes si quieren rescatar a las criaturas liberadas y derrotar al serpenteante villano.

title: El Laberinto del Dragon Rojo
description: Aún en la zona de juego de Tierra Karana, Okino tiene que elegir entre ayudar a sus aliados ninjas, u obedecer las órdenes de su Maestro, Unagami.

title: Pato Underwater
description: Pato packs his bag of toys and heads off to play with Octopus and Whale underwater. Unfortunately none of his toys work in the sea, and he doesn't like the food so he's all set to head back home. But then Whale shows Pato how fun things can be underwater once you get used to it. Pato has a wonderful time riding on Whale's back, bouncing on sea sponges and playing in a bubble. Finally Pocoyo and Elly arrive too and everyone has a splashy underwater party together.

title: The Maze of the Red Dragon
description: Still in the game zone Terra Kerana, the Samurai guide Okino has to choose between helping his allies the ninja, or obeying the evil orders of his Master, Unagami.

title: Heatwave
description: Apple and Onion try to spread cheer during a city-wide heatwave.

title: Los Acantilados de la Histeria
description: Los Ninjas suben a los Acantilados de la histeria y descubren que Unagami convierte a los jugadores en cubos de energía para construir un portal.

title: Birthday Bash/Too Pooped to Puff
description: Birthday Bash: It's the girls birthday and some special presents have arrived from the girls' main enemies. Can they destroy these evil gifts without destroying their party?/Too Pooped to Puff: The girls become exhausted when the town begins to over use them. They go on strike and end up teaching the townspeople how to fend for themselves.

title: Home Sweet Hole
description: When Vic won't share and play nice with his buddies it escalates to an all-out war. Will he learn to share, or will his selfishness bury them all under tons of dirt.

title: Brain Freeze
description: When a mysterious new ice cream flavor takes Townsville by storm, the girls suspect there might be foul play.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Follow the North Star
description: The boys' quest becomes a battle against self-doubt, when Victor and Valentino discover that the only way to defeat Tez is to seek out a powerful ancient entity.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: The Very Best Candy
description: The gang can't decide which of their candy is the best, so they turn it sentient and have it fight to determine the winner.
